txt.en: Gellamiel can be found in Ost Galadh.\n\nYou should speak with Gellamiel.
Roving Threat: Helchurth, the Eternal Shadow
Elite lieutenants of Dol Guldur have been seen patrolling the hostile region of Southern Mirkwood, including Helchurth, an eternal servant of the Nazgul.
Helchurth can be found somewhere in Southern Mirkwood.\n\nYou should defeat Helchurth.
'The forces of Dol Guldur may outnumber us but our hope outshines all. You have done a great service for the Malledhrim.'

'I have seen black robes in the night, wandering with soundless footsteps. The Cargûls of Dol Guldur are equally sad and dangerous wraiths. Any [placeholder] should heed caution when encountering a Cargûl. This warning holds true to Helchurth, a truly terrifying minion of the enemy. Tread carefully or this apparition will trick you.'
